                                    <p>MSME loans in the Philippines are financial products specifically designed for Micro, Small, and Medium Enterprises (MSMEs). These loans offer smaller amounts compared to loans for larger businesses. They are crucial because MSMEs play a key role in driving economic growth and creating jobs, yet they often face challenges in accessing financing from traditional sources.</p>
